@node Introduction "RandPic Documentation - Introduction"

@{b}RandPic@{ub} is a small program that provides random backdrop pictures.

It runs from the startup-sequence each boot up and picks a random picture
from the specified directory.

@endnode

@node Requirements "RandPic Documentation - Requirements"

@{b}RandPic@{ub} requires an Amiga capable of displaying a backdrop picture.
@endnode

@node Distribution "RandPic Documentation - Distribution"




