@endnode

@node Installation "RandPic Documentation - Installation"

To install @{b}RandPic@{ub}, just copy the RandPic program to the C: directory.

Next edit the file S:startup-sequence and add the following line somewhere
@{b}before@{ub} C:IPrefs
    C:RandPic <PicDir>
where PicDir is the directory that you have your backdrop pictures in eg.
    C:RandPic sys:backdrops

Reboot the Amiga and run the WBPattern prefs program and select the file
'sys:.BackPic' as your backdrop picture.

Next time you reboot you will have a different backdrop (hopefully :-)
@endnode

@node Bugs "RandPic Documentation - Bugs"

There are no known bugs with @{b}RandPic@{ub} (Famous last words ... :),
but if you find one @{"drop me a line" link Author}.
@endnode

